<h2 id="download" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0">Download Sonic Colors Demastered</h2>

<strong>Version 0.5.4</strong> includes all 5 zones, the full wisp roster, Jukebox mode, New Game+, and the Skill Shop system. The 909 MB download also bundles the game's original soundtrack as a separate ZIP file.

